- **No HTTPS enforcement.** Terminate TLS at a proxy, but also add `app.use((req, res, next) => req.secure || req.headers['x-forwarded-proto'] === 'https' ? next() : res.redirect('https://' + req.headers.host + req.url));` when behind one.
